---
// Article 6.6: Grants and Funding
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../../components/Footer.astro';
import AudienceTabs from '../../../components/AudienceTabs.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../../../components/panduan-rakyat/Breadcrumb';

const articleData = {
  sectionNumber: '06',
  sectionTitle: 'Starting a Business',
  sectionIcon: '🚀',
  articleTitle: 'Grants and Funding: MSMEs, Startups and Tech Startups',
  articleDescription: 'MSME grants, startup grants, equity funding options',
  colorRgb: '234, 88, 12',
  lastUpdated: 'March 2026',
};

const simpleContent = `
  <h2 id="funding-options">Funding options for businesses:</h2>
  <p>There are many ways to get money for your business.</p>
  
  <h2 id="grants">Grants (free money):</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Don't need to pay back</li>
    <li>For specific purposes</li>
    <li>Must meet criteria</li>
    <li>Submit proposal</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="loans">Loans (borrowed money):</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Must pay back with interest</li>
    <li>Banks and government schemes</li>
    <li>Need good credit</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="equity">Equity (selling shares):</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Sell part of your company</li>
    <li>Investors become partners</li>
    <li>No repayment but share profits</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="where-to-apply">Where to apply:</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>SME Corp</li>
    <li>MARA</li>
    <li>TEKUN</li>
    <li>Banks</li>
    <li>Investors</li>
  </ul>
`;

const detailedContent = `
  <h2 id="overview">Overview</h2>
  <p>Funding is crucial for business growth. Malaysia offers various funding options from grants to equity.</p>

  <h2 id="msme-grants">MSME Grants</h2>
  <h3>SME Corp Programmes:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Matching Grant:</strong> 50-70% matching for automation</li>
    <li><strong>Digitalisation Grant:</strong> For digital tools adoption</li>
    <li><strong>Business Digitalisation Initiative:</strong> E-commerce, digital marketing</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>MARA Programmes:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Usahawan MARA:</strong> For Bumiputera entrepreneurs</li>
    <li><strong>Micro Credit Financing:</strong> Up to RM50,000</li>
    <li><strong>Franchise Development:</strong> For franchise businesses</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="startup-funding">Startup Funding</h2>
  <h3>Government Programmes:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>MRANTI:</strong> Deep tech startups</li>
    <li><strong>Cradle Fund:</strong> Early-stage startups</li>
    <li><strong>MAVCAP:</strong> Venture capital</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Tech Startup Specific:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>MDEC Grants:</strong> Digital economy startups</li>
    <li><strong>GAIN:</strong> Global Accelerator and Innovation Network</li>
    <li><strong>NEXEA:</strong> Angel investor network</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="equity-funding">Equity Funding</h2>
  <h3>Angel Investors:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Individual investors</li>
    <li>Early-stage investment</li>
    <li>RM100k - RM2M typical</li>
    <li>Also provide mentorship</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Venture Capital:</h3>
    <li>Professional investment firms</li>
    <li>Growth-stage companies</li>
    <li>RM2M+ investment</li>
    <li>Board seat common</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="funding-comparison">Funding Comparison</h2>
  <table class="w-full border-collapse border border-border my-4">
    <thead><tr class="bg-muted"><th class="border border-border p-3 text-left">Type</th><th class="border border-border p-3 text-left">Amount</th><th class="border border-border p-3 text-left">Repayment</th><th class="border border-border p-3 text-left">Best For</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td class="border border-border p-3">Grants</td><td class="border border-border p-3">RM10k-RM500k</td><td class="border border-border p-3">None</td><td class="border border-border p-3">Specific projects</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="border border-border p-3">Bank Loans</td><td class="border border-border p-3">RM50k-RM5M</td><td class="border border-border p-3">With interest</td><td class="border border-border p-3">Established businesses</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="border border-border p-3">Angel Investment</td><td class="border border-border p-3">RM100k-RM2M</td><td class="border border-border p-3">Equity</td><td class="border border-border p-3">Early startups</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="border border-border p-3">VC</td><td class="border border-border p-3">RM2M+</td><td class="border border-border p-3">Equity</td><td class="border border-border p-3">Growth stage</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2 id="how-to-apply">How to Apply</h2>
  <ol>
    <li><strong>Prepare business plan:</strong> Clear vision and financials</li>
    <li><strong>Check eligibility:</strong> Match programme criteria</li>
    <li><strong>Submit application:</strong> Follow guidelines</li>
    <li><strong>Pitch presentation:</strong> If shortlisted</li>
    <li><strong>Due diligence:</strong> Investor verification</li>
    <li><strong>Receive funding:</strong> Agreement signing</li>
  </ol>

  <h2 id="important-numbers">Important Contacts</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>SME Corp:</strong> 03-6201 2000</li>
    <li><strong>MARA:</strong> 03-2610 2000</li>
    <li><strong>MDEC:</strong> 03-8315 3000</li>
    <li><strong>Cradle:</strong> 03-7968 8888</li>
  </ul>
`;

const faqs = [
  {
    question: "What's the difference between grant and loan?",
    answer: "Grants don't need repayment but have strict usage requirements. Loans must be repaid with interest but offer more flexibility."
  },
  {
    question: "How much equity should I give investors?",
    answer: "Early stage: 10-25%. Series A: 20-40%. Depends on valuation, amount raised, and negotiation. Don't give away too much too early."
  },
  {
    question: "How long does grant approval take?",
    answer: "Varies: SME Corp grants 1-3 months. MARA loans 2-4 weeks. Equity funding 3-6 months (includes due diligence)."
  },
  {
    question: "Can I apply for multiple funding sources?",
    answer: "Yes, but disclose all applications. Some grants cannot be combined. Equity investors may have exclusivity requirements."
  }
];

const headings = [
  { id: 'overview', title: 'Overview', level: 2 },
  { id: 'msme-grants', title: 'MSME Grants', level: 2 },
  { id: 'startup-funding', title: 'Startup Funding', level: 2 },
  { id: 'equity-funding', title: 'Equity Funding', level: 2 },
  { id: 'funding-comparison', title: 'Funding Comparison', level: 2 },
  { id: 'how-to-apply', title: 'How to Apply', level: 2 },
];
---

<Layout title={`${articleData.articleTitle} | People's Guide | EduLaluan`}>
  <Header />
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-background">
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-section-lg border-b" style={{'--section-color': `rgb(${articleData.colorRgb})`,'border-bottom-color': `rgb(${articleData.colorRgb})`}}>
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-4xl">
          <Breadcrumb items={[{label:'Home',href:'/'},{label:"People's Guide",href:'/panduan-rakyat'},{label:`Section ${articleData.sectionNumber}`,href:`/panduan-rakyat/section-${articleData.sectionNumber}`},{label:articleData.articleTitle}]} />
          <a href={`/panduan-rakyat/section-${articleData.sectionNumber}`} class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-primary transition-colors mb-6"><svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" /></svg>Back to Section {parseInt(articleData.sectionNumber).toString()}</a>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mt-6"><div class="flex h-16 w-16 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-xl text-3xl" style={{'backgroundColor': `rgb(${articleData.colorRgb})`,'color': 'white'}}>{articleData.sectionIcon}</div><div class="flex-1"><p class="text-sm font-medium text-primary mb-1 tracking-wide uppercase">Section {parseInt(articleData.sectionNumber).toString()}: {articleData.sectionTitle}</p><h1 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-foreground">{articleData.articleTitle}</h1><p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground mt-3">{articleData.articleDescription}</p></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="py-section-md bg-surface">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="flex gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <AudienceTabs>
              <Fragment slot="simple" set:html={simpleContent} />
              <Fragment slot="detailed" set:html={detailedContent} />
            </AudienceTabs>
            <div class="mt-12"><h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class="space-y-3">{faqs.map((faq)=>(<details class="group rounded-xl border bg-surface-elevated transition-all"><summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between p-5 font-semibold text-foreground list-none">{faq.question}<svg class="h-5 w-5 text-muted-foreground transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" /></svg></summary><div class="px-5 pb-5 text-muted-foreground">{faq.answer}</div></details>))}</div></div>
            <div class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-border"><p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground"><strong>Last updated:</strong> {articleData.lastUpdated}</p></div>
          </div>
          <aside class="sticky top-24 hidden lg:block w-64 shrink-0"><nav class="space-y-1" aria-label="Table of contents"><h3 class="text-xs font-semibold text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">On This Page</h3>{headings.map((heading)=>(<a href={`#${heading.id}`} class="block py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors" style={{paddingLeft:`${(heading.level-2)*12+12}px`}}>{heading.title}</a>))}</nav></aside>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="py-section-md bg-background"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl"><div class="rounded-2xl border bg-surface-elevated p-6"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-muted-foreground"><svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg><p class="text-sm"><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> This guide provides general information only. Always verify with official sources for the most current information.</p></div></div></div></div></section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
<style>:root{--section-padding-lg:clamp(3rem,5vw + 1rem,5rem);--section-padding-md:clamp(2rem,3vw + 1rem,3rem)}.py-section-lg{padding-top:var(--section-padding-lg);padding-bottom:var(--section-padding-lg)}.py-section-md{padding-top:var(--section-padding-md);padding-bottom:var(--section-padding-md)}.prose-panduan{font-size:var(--text-base);line-height:var(--leading-relaxed);color:var(--foreground)}.prose-panduan h2{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:var(--text-2xl);font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;color:var(--foreground)}.prose-panduan h3{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:var(--text-xl);font-weight:600;margin-top:2rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem;color:var(--foreground)}.prose-panduan p{margin-bottom:1.25rem}.prose-panduan ul,.prose-panduan ol{margin-bottom:1.25rem;padding-left:1.5rem}.prose-panduan li{margin-bottom:0.5rem}.prose-panduan a{color:var(--primary);text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:2px}.prose-panduan a:hover{color:var(--primary-dark)}.prose-panduan strong{font-weight:600;color:var(--foreground)}.prose-panduan table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:1.5rem 0}.prose-panduan th{background-color:var(--muted);font-weight:600;padding:0.75rem;border:1px solid var(--border)}.prose-panduan td{padding:0.75rem;border:1px solid var(--border)}.prose-panduan .bg-muted{background-color:var(--muted);padding:1rem;border-radius:0.5rem;margin:1.5rem 0}</style>
